data.description: ***BEAUTIFUL WATERFRONT HOME CLOSE TO SHOPPING, RESTAURANTS, AND MORE!!!*** Situated on a large, quarter acre lot, this Florida Style Cottage exudes charm and warmth and has been beautifully updated with vinyl plank flooring, neutral paint, beautiful kitchen cabinets, butcher block countertops, stainless steel appliances, a farmhouse style sink, custom tiled backsplash and bathrooms, gorgeous new vanities, and updated fixtures. The open-concept living area is a perfect gathering spot and there is a large Bonus Room off the dining area that would make an excellent office, den, or hobby room. The fenced back yard provides plenty of space for pets or kids and even has a shed with a good foundation that could be your mancave or she shed. The roof and AC are only 4 years old. Solar panels were recently installed which means super low electric bills! (Bill has been $29.98 mo.) No HOA plus this home is located in Flood Zone X so no flood insurance is required. City water and sewer. Only 14 minutes to Tyndall AFB, 12 minutes to Sacred Heart, 21 minutes to Naval Support Activity (NSA) Panama City, and 24 minutes to The World's Most Beautiful Beaches. A very nice ADT security system will also convey with the property. Great home with all the extras just waiting on its new owner! CALL TODAY FOR MORE INFORMATION OR TO SCHEDULE YOUR PRIVATE TOUR!
